      <title>马克龙和肖尔茨最后一刻的举动激怒了峰会上的欧盟领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/macron-and-scholz-s-summit-hijack-hits-a-wall-of-angry-eu-leaders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国和德国习惯于在欧盟舞台上为所欲为。但当欧盟最大的两个经济体周四出席至关重要的欧盟峰会时，却因国内问题而分心，他们发现很难再施展影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/macron-and-scholz-s-summit-hijack-hits-a-wall-of-angry-eu-leaders</guid>
